                  2003. 12.  “The Face of the Past: Memory and Forgetting  in The Bonesetter’s Daughter.” Negotiating the Past: An International  Conference on Asia American and Asian British  Literatures. Taipei:  Academia Sinica.

                  2004. 03.  ＜反全球化運動：跨國抗爭幽靈的時間、空間與語言＞。「建構批判性的跨（國）文化流動研究學術研討會」。交通大學通識中心。 

                  2004. 06.  “On the Spectrality of Anti-Globalization.” The  Fifth International Crossroads in Cultural Studies Conference. Illinois: the University   of Illinois.

                  2004. 08.  “The Economy of Postmodern Diaspora.” The  2004 Congress of the International Comparative Literature Association.Hong Kong: International Comparative Literature  Association.

                  2004. 12.  “Post-Magical Realism as Critical History in  Toni Morrison’s Beloved.” Conference on Toni Morrison. Taipei: Academia Sinica.

                  2005. 09.  ＜論（無）耐心救世主主義＞。「兩岸哲學與宗教文化研討會」。南京大學哲學系。 
                  2005. 12.  “Narrative as a Mode of Counter Theory in  Story, Theory, and Truth.” The Eighth  International Conference of the Forum on Contemporary Theory. India: Louisiana  University and Mangalore University.

                  2006. 03.  ＜友誼政治與父權治理＞。「禪．藝術．管理與現代中國研討會」。南華大學世界禪學研究中心。 
                  2006. 09.  “On Violence: Derrida, Levinas and Benjamin.”  Hangzhou  International Conference on Levinas. Hangzhou: Zhe-Jiang University,  The Forum for European Philosophy and The Levinas Ethical Legacy Foundation.

                  2006. 09. ＜論典範的不可共量性：孔恩與卡維爾＞。「文藝典範與創意研發學術研討會」。成功大學文學院。 
                  2007.06 “(Im)Patient Messianism: Marx, Levinas and  Derrida.” The Second Annual Conference of  the North American Levinas Society. Indianapolis:  Purdue University.

